name: Stockholm Industrial Exhibition 1866
obverse: Bust of Oscar I facing right.
obverse_inscriptions: OSCAR SVERIGES O. NORGES ARFFURSTE HERT. AF ÖSTERG. *
reverse_inscriptions: SVERIGE, NORGE, DANMARK OCH FINLAND I FREDLIG TÄFLAN 1866.
description: This medal was made to commemorate the industrial exhibition held in Stockholm in 1866.
This medal was minted in the exhibition building and sold to visitors.
